snippet.title: Block Strategy - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Block Strategy is an upcoming singleplayer RTS game with a fully destructible world. Now launching on the 30th of September 2024 on Steam. 

You can wishlist Block Strategy on steam here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2642070/Block_Strategy/

#gaming   #rts #indiegame #realtimestrategy #realtimestrategygames
